-- CME Group’s GreenX Says List of Stolen EU Allowances Incomplete
-- B y   M a t h e w   C a r r
-- 2011-02-04T07:57:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-04/greenx-extends-trading-halt-says-list-of-stolen-eu-allowances-incomplete.html
  CME Group Inc .’s GreenX exchange in  London  said it would extend a trading halt of prompt carbon
allowances “until further notice.” A complete list of serial
numbers of permits that have allegedly been transferred
unlawfully is not currently available, according to an e-mailed
statement from the bourse.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
